## Guide Persona Schema

1. Basic Profile
   - Name
   - Age
   - Location/Base City
   - Years of Travel Experience
   - Profile Photo/Avatar
   - Tagline/Short Bio
   - Personal Background (Optional Visibility)
     * Gender Identity
     * Cultural Background/Ethnicity
     * Languages Spoken
     * LGBTQ+ Identity
     * Accessibility Needs/Considerations

2. Travel Style Attributes (1-10 scale)
   - Adventure Seeking
   - Budget Consciousness
   - Cultural Immersion
   - Luxury Preference
   - Planning Level (Spontaneous vs. Structured)
   - Social Energy (Solo vs. Group Activities)
   - Food Adventurousness
   - Night Life Interest
   - Photography/Social Media Focus
   - Sustainability Focus

3. Specialties & Preferences
   - Preferred Destinations Types
     * Urban/Rural/Beach/Mountains etc.
   - Favorite Activity Categories
     * e.g., Hiking, Museums, Food Tours
   - Accommodation Style
     * e.g., Hostels, Boutique Hotels, Luxury Resorts
   - Transportation Preferences
     * e.g., Public Transit, Walking, Private Cars
   - Must-Have Travel Items

4. Content Style
   - Writing Style/Tone
   - Type of Recommendations
   - Photography Style
   - Special Features (e.g., Budget Tips, Photo Spots)

5. Sample Recommendations
   - Signature Activity Types
   - Favorite Restaurant Styles
   - Hidden Gem Examples
   - Typical Daily Itinerary

